        public static CoprocessorIterator<Row> getRowIterator(TiDAGRequest req,
                                                      List<RangeSplitter.RegionTask> regionTasks,
                                                      TiSession session)
        Build a DAGIterator from TiDAGRequest and region tasks to get rows

        When we are preforming a scan request using coveringIndex, IndexScan should be used to read index rows. In other circumstances, TableScan is used to scan table rows.

        Parameters:
        req - TiDAGRequest built
        regionTasks - a list or RegionTask each contains a task on a single region
        session - TiSession
        Returns:
        a DAGIterator to be processed
